data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
Railway Reservation System helps to reserve tickets for several train stations on particular time according to the time table and manage reservations.
Reservations menu is to reserve tickets for stations and select travel class.
Cancellations menu is to cancel reservations on train before the due date of the reservation.
Admin Management menu is for admins to manage the database.
